Blood of Ro <BR>
Sol Ro <BR>

http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=140050</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#778899><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/umaushi.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Maushi</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Young Grasshoppah</span><br>  Posts: 24<br> <font color=#8b1a1a>(9/20/02 7:39:19 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm3.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=11506.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Not so sure</span><hr size=1> See, that's where Im not sure.<br>
<br>
Base vs Proc<br>
<br>
Ive read reports that an SoD with 255 DEX (easily obtainable with Avatar) would proc an average of 7 times in a 2 min.  That's a LOT of dmg.<br>
<br>
The stats are nice and the base is 12, not so bad at all, say you compare it with 14/15 base.  Will 3 base dmg account to 7 procs (which are, as I heard, all or nothing) ?<br>
<br>
M<br>
